    <h2>Who am I?</h2>
    <p>As you may know; <em>I am ReyonC</em>. But you can address me as Rey.</p>
    <fieldset class="fieldset-left">
      <p>My family comes from an I.T. background and I always believed I would be different. I took a <strong>physical direction</strong>, worked  at labour jobs as maintenance, factory works, carpentry, metal worker  etc.
    </fieldset>
    <fieldset class="fieldset-mid">
      <p>Not finding my zone in Physical labour, I tried to pursue a different path. I tried <em>fitness</em> and a little <em>freelance</em> modeling. Truth be told, it is a difficult path and you meet a lot of strange people. It appears it wasn't for me.</p>
  </fieldset>
  <fieldset class="fieldset-right">
   <p>Realising I have to look more inward, I really like spending time on the computer "building" stuff, I tried to pursue this way. I.T. is a broad topic and there are countless of paths. I found my interest here.
